@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Get all events (filtered by city)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?city=Munich

### Get all events (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?page=1&pageSize=5

### Get event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1

### Get event sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/sessions

### Create event (valid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechConf 2026",
  "date": "2026-09-15",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "Premier tech conference"
}

### Create event (invalid - should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "date": "2020-01-01",
  "city": ""
}

### Update event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechConf 2026 Updated",
  "date": "2026-09-16",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "Updated"
}

### Delete event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1

### Get non-existent event (should return 404 ProblemDetails)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/999
